This is a set of programs and created data for COMP433 (Information Retrieval).
The programs are written by Robert Luk and they should only be used for COMP433.

compile		The script that compiles the program (using g++ compiler)
stem		The Porter stemming algorithm
IInvFile	The integrated inverted index class (declaration/definition)
BuildInvFile	Converts the data in post.txt into the inverted file format
		using the integrated inverted index class
DocLen		Computes the document length of each document (should be used
		after BuildInvFile is run or the InvFile.txt is created)
Retrieval	Perform interactive retrieval (should be used after BuildInvFile
		and DocLen are run, or the InvFile.txt and InvFile.doc are
		created)

